data.description: This sprawling property offers the perfect blend of rural tranquility and modern convenience. Situated on generous acreage, this home boasts both a comfortable living space and a spacious shop for all your hobbies and storage needs. The home itself is a charming retreat featuring multiple bedrooms, bright & open living areas, downstairs theatre room & outdoor entertainment area w/large patio & tiered Trex decks w/a hot tub & built in bar. One of the standout features of this property is the expansive shop. Whether you're a car enthusiast, a woodworker, or simply need ample space for storage, this shop/office is a dream come true. Bonus features include 30-amp power RV hook up & business entrance conveniently located off of Hwy 20.
